<h2 id="installing-and-importing-packages">Installing and Importing Packages</h2>

<p>To install an R package:</p>
<div class="language-R highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">intall.packages</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"âŸ¨package_nameâŸ©"</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>To import package:</p>
<div class="language-R highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">library</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="err">âŸ¨</span><span class="n">package_name</span><span class="err">âŸ©</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div></div>

